Have you tried the LOC Method?

The L.O.C Method is a regimen our CEO came up with back in 2011.
The acronym stands for...

L - Liquid Leave In Conditioner
O - Oil
C - Cream

This method will seal the moisture in your hair for an extended period of time.

We have several L.O.C. Kits available at www.alikaynaturals.com! 🥰
